highlights.text: “เจ้าของที่ (My Favorite)” by Mirrr has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 1259 days straight.
Saran has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “รออยู่อย่างนั้น” is the highest at #29.
“จังหวะจะรัก” by Violette Wautier is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 65 spots at #53.
“เรียกว่ารักได้ไหม (Is This Love?)” by GEMINI and FOURTH is the highest new entry on Top Songs Thailand at #144.
